What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: a way to get credit for your work in lab but you don't get a letter grade anymore which is so stupid.
If you're doing research might as well, but now it's pass/fail for non-seniors so not really much use...
A great fifth class and an awesome introduction to research or a continuation of your summer research experience. Pick your PI wisely and you're good to go.
Don't bother taking this if it's still P/F. Take another class instead and do research on the side.
